<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Pitt Pre-Law | Law School Data Guide 2022–2025</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700;900&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Roboto+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --pitt-blue: #003594;
    --pitt-gold: #FFB81C;
    --pitt-dark: #001f5b;
    --pitt-mid-blue: #1a4b8c;
    --ink: #1a1a2e;
    --muted: #5a6378;
    --rule: #d0d8e8;
    --bg: #f7f8fc;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --positive: #0e7c3a;
    --positive-bg: #e6f4ec;
    --negative: #c0392b;
    --negative-bg: #fdecea;
    --neutral: #4a5568;
    --neutral-bg: #edf2f7;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.5; min-height: 100vh; }

  .masthead { background: var(--pitt-blue); border-bottom: 4px solid var(--pitt-gold); padding: 28px 40px 22px; display: flex; align-items: flex-end; justify-content: space-between; gap: 20px; }
  .masthead-left { flex: 1; }
  .masthead-eyebrow { font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--pitt-gold); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .masthead-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--white); line-height: 1.1; }
  .masthead-title span { color: var(--pitt-gold); }
  .masthead-sub { font-size: 13px; color: #e8d48a; margin-top: 6px; font-weight: 300; }
  .masthead-right { text-align: right; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .masthead-badge { display: inline-block; background: var(--pitt-gold); color: var(--pitt-dark); font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 12px; padding: 5px 12px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
  .masthead-note { font-size: 11px; color: #e8d48a; margin-top: 6px; }

  .nav-tabs { background: var(--pitt-blue); display: flex; padding: 0 40px; overflow-x: auto; }
  .tab-btn { font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #e8d48a; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 14px 20px 12px; border-bottom: 3px solid transparent; white-space: nowrap; transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s; }
  .tab-btn:hover { color: #ffffff; }
  .tab-btn.active { color: var(--pitt-gold); border-bottom-color: var(--pitt-gold); }

  .section-panel { display: none; padding: 32px 40px 48px; }
  .section-panel.active { display: block; }
  .section-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--pitt-dark); margin-bottom: 6px; text-align: center; }
  .section-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 20px; max-width: 700px; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

  .stat-strip { display: flex; margin-bottom: 24px; border: 1px solid var(--rule); border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden; background: var(--white); }
  .stat-item { flex: 1; padding: 16px 20px; border-right: 1px solid var(--rule); text-align: center; }
  .stat-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .stat-label { font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .stat-value { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--pitt-dark); }
  .stat-value.sm { font-size: 17px; }
  .stat-sub { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px; }

  .controls-bar { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 18px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .controls-bar label { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; color: var(--muted); }
  .search-input { font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; border: 1.5px solid var(--rule); border-radius: 4px; padding: 6px 12px; width: 220px; background: var(--white); color: var(--ink); outline: none; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
  .search-input:focus { border-color: var(--pitt-blue); }
  .limit-select { font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; border: 1.5px solid var(--rule); border-radius: 4px; padding: 6px 10px; background: var(--white); color: var(--ink); cursor: pointer; outline: none; }

  .data-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13.5px; }
  .data-table thead tr { background: var(--pitt-dark); color: var(--white); }
  .data-table thead th { font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 500; padding: 10px 14px; text-align: center; white-space: nowrap; cursor: pointer; user-select: none; }
  .data-table thead th:hover { background: var(--pitt-mid-blue); }
  .data-table thead th.sort-active { color: var(--pitt-gold); }
  .data-table tbody tr { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); transition: background 0.1s; }
  .data-table tbody tr:hover { background: #f0f4fb; }
  .data-table tbody tr:nth-child(even) { background: #fafbfd; }
  .data-table tbody tr:nth-child(even):hover { background: #f0f4fb; }
  .data-table td { padding: 10px 14px; vertical-align: middle; text-align: center; }

  .rank-num { font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--muted); width: 32px; text-align: center; }
  .school-name { font-weight: 600; color: var(--pitt-dark); font-size: 13.5px; }
  .num-cell { font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; text-align: center; color: var(--ink); }
  .sort-ind { margin-left: 4px; opacity: 0.5; }
  .sort-ind.on { opacity: 1; color: var(--pitt-gold); }

  .pct-badge { display: inline-block; font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 10px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .pct-badge.high { background: var(--positive-bg); color: var(--positive); }
  .pct-badge.med  { background: #fff3cd; color: #7a5a00; }
  .pct-badge.low  { background: var(--negative-bg); color: var(--negative); }

  .diff-badge { display: inline-block; font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace; font-size: 11.5px; font-weight: 500; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 10px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .diff-pos { background: var(--positive-bg); color: var(--positive); }
  .diff-neg { background: var(--negative-bg); color: var(--negative); }
  .diff-neu { background: var(--neutral-bg); color: var(--neutral); }

  .filter-chips { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 16px; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .chip-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .5px; }
  .chip { font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; border: 1.5px solid var(--rule); border-radius: 20px; padding: 4px 12px; background: var(--white); color: var(--muted); cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s; }
  .chip:hover { border-color: var(--pitt-blue); color: var(--pitt-blue); }
  .chip.active { background: var(--pitt-blue); border-color: var(--pitt-blue); color: var(--white); }
  .chip.pos-filter.active { background: var(--positive); border-color: var(--positive); }
  .chip.neg-filter.active { background: var(--negative); border-color: var(--negative); }

  .rate-legend { display: flex; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 18px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .legend-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); }
  .legend-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .dot-pitt { background: var(--pitt-blue); }
  .dot-nat  { background: #aab8cc; }
  .dot-pos  { background: var(--positive); }
  .dot-neg  { background: var(--negative); }

  .no-results { padding: 32px; text-align: center; color: var(--muted); font-style: italic; }
  .footnote { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 11.5px; color: var(--muted); border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); padding-top: 12px; line-height: 1.7; }
  .footnote strong { color: var(--pitt-dark); }

  /* ── TOOLTIP ── */
  .tip-wrap { position: relative; display: inline-block; }
  .tip-wrap .school-name { border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--muted); cursor: default; }
  .tooltip {
    display: none;
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; top: calc(100% + 6px);
    z-index: 100;
    background: var(--pitt-dark);
    color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    min-width: 260px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .tip-wrap:hover .tooltip { display: block; }
  .tooltip-title { font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--pitt-gold); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .tip-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 3px 10px; }
  .tip-grid .th { font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #94a8cc; }
  .tip-grid .yr { font-weight: 600; color: var(--pitt-gold); font-size: 11px; }
  .tip-grid .val { font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: var(--white); }
  .tip-grid .na { font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #5a6378; }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .masthead { padding: 20px 16px; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    .section-panel { padding: 20px 16px 40px; }
    .nav-tabs { padding: 0 16px; }
    .stat-strip { flex-direction: column; }
    .stat-item { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
    .search-input { width: 100%; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="masthead">
  <div class="masthead-left">
    <div class="masthead-eyebrow">University of Pittsburgh · Pre-Law Advising</div>
    <div class="masthead-title">Law School <span>Application Data</span></div>
    <div class="masthead-sub">Where Pitt undergrads applied, were admitted, and enrolled · Three-year trend data (2022–2025)</div>
  </div>
  <div class="masthead-right">
    <div class="masthead-badge">2022–2025 Data Guide</div>
    <div class="masthead-note">Source: LSAC & ABA First-Year Class Reports</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="nav-tabs">
  <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="showTab('overview', this)">Application Overview</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('rates', this)">Acceptance Rates vs. National</button>
</div>

<!-- OVERVIEW PANEL -->
<div id="panel-overview" class="section-panel active">
  <div class="section-title">Where Pitt Students Applied, Were Admitted &amp; Enrolled</div>
  <div class="section-desc">All law schools where Pitt undergraduates applied over the 2022–2025 cycle. Click any column header to sort. Hover a school name to see the year-by-year breakdown. Pitt Admit Rate is color-coded: <span class="pct-badge high">≥40%</span> <span class="pct-badge med">20–39%</span> <span class="pct-badge low">&lt;20%</span></div>

  <div class="stat-strip" id="stats-overview"></div>

  <div class="controls-bar">
    <label>Show</label>
    <select class="limit-select" id="limit-overview" onchange="renderOverview()">
      <option value="25">Top 25</option>
      <option value="50">Top 50</option>
      <option value="999">All</option>
    </select>
    <label>Search</label>
    <input class="search-input" id="search-overview" placeholder="Filter by school name…" oninput="renderOverview()">
  </div>

  <table class="data-table" id="table-overview">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th onclick="sortOverview('rank')"># <span class="sort-ind on" id="ind-ov-rank">↓</span></th>
        <th onclick="sortOverview('name')">School <span class="sort-ind" id="ind-ov-name"></span></th>
        <th onclick="sortOverview('apps')">Applications <span class="sort-ind on" id="ind-ov-apps">↓</span></th>
        <th onclick="sortOverview('admitted')">Admitted <span class="sort-ind" id="ind-ov-admitted"></span></th>
        <th onclick="sortOverview('matric')">Matriculated <span class="sort-ind" id="ind-ov-matric"></span></th>
        <th onclick="sortOverview('pitt_rate')">Pitt Admit Rate <span class="sort-ind" id="ind-ov-pitt_rate"></span></th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody id="tbody-overview"></tbody>
  </table>
  <div class="footnote">
    <strong>Applications</strong> = total Pitt undergrads who submitted an application to each school across all three years. &nbsp;
    <strong>Admitted</strong> = offers of admission received. &nbsp;
    <strong>Matriculated</strong> = students who enrolled. &nbsp;
    <strong>Pitt Admit Rate</strong> = admitted ÷ applications from Pitt undergrads over the full three-year period.
  </div>
</div>

<!-- RATES PANEL -->
<div id="panel-rates" class="section-panel">
  <div class="section-title">Pitt Acceptance Rate vs. National Average</div>
  <div class="section-desc">Compares how each school admitted Pitt applicants against its overall national acceptance rate (ABA data, 2023–2025 combined). Only schools with ≥15 Pitt applications and available national data are shown.</div>

  <div class="stat-strip" id="stats-rates"></div>

  <div class="rate-legend">
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot dot-pos"></div>Pitt exceeds national</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot dot-neg"></div>National exceeds Pitt</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--neutral)"></div>Within 3% of national</div>
  </div>

  <div class="filter-chips">
    <span class="chip-label">Filter:</span>
    <button class="chip active" id="chip-all" onclick="setRateFilter('all')">All Schools</button>
    <button class="chip pos-filter" id="chip-pos" onclick="setRateFilter('pos')">Pitt Above Average</button>
    <button class="chip neg-filter" id="chip-neg" onclick="setRateFilter('neg')">Pitt Below Average</button>
  </div>

  <div class="controls-bar">
    <label>Show</label>
    <select class="limit-select" id="limit-rates" onchange="renderRates()">
      <option value="25">Top 25 by Apps</option>
      <option value="50">Top 50 by Apps</option>
      <option value="999">All</option>
    </select>
    <label>Search</label>
    <input class="search-input" id="search-rates" placeholder="Filter by school name…" oninput="renderRates()">
  </div>

  <table class="data-table" id="table-rates">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th onclick="sortRates('rank')"># <span class="sort-ind on" id="ind-rt-rank">↓</span></th>
        <th onclick="sortRates('name')">School <span class="sort-ind" id="ind-rt-name"></span></th>
        <th onclick="sortRates('apps')">Pitt Apps <span class="sort-ind" id="ind-rt-apps"></span></th>
        <th onclick="sortRates('pitt_rate')">Pitt Rate <span class="sort-ind" id="ind-rt-pitt_rate"></span></th>
        <th onclick="sortRates('nat_rate')">National Rate <span class="sort-ind" id="ind-rt-nat_rate"></span></th>
        <th onclick="sortRates('diff')">Difference <span class="sort-ind" id="ind-rt-diff"></span></th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody id="tbody-rates"></tbody>
  </table>
  <div class="footnote">
    <strong>Pitt Rate</strong> = Pitt applicants admitted ÷ Pitt applicants (three-year total). &nbsp;
    <strong>National Rate</strong> = all applicants admitted nationally (ABA First-Year Class data, 2023–2025 combined). &nbsp;
    <strong>Difference</strong> = Pitt rate minus national rate. Positive values mean Pitt applicants were admitted at above-average rates.
  </div>
</div>

